##### Please visit my blog to know what I am doing! It's in Polish language! [>>Masogs blog<<](http://masog.wordpress.com "")

v1:
- Added one missing texture..
- I can't fix textures bug... If someone know how to fix it, I will be happy.
- I think that bug with spawn is fixed.
- Added 4 hegrenades at the top.
- Deleted music.

This is Knife Arena map, created for the Battle of Details contest (not from GameBanana). The theme of the contest is Science Fiction. This is a really big Knife Arena map. On my map here are some ropes and you can climb on them. Here are two "flying cars" and they are controlled by auto-pilot. 

I did this map in 4 days.

This is perfect map for minigames server. Yea, I know, this is KA map, not MG - but here are a lot of fun! 

- TT spawns: 24.
- CT spawns: 24.
- "Flying Cars": 2.
- Ropes: about 100.
- Textures: Portal by reacz.
- Music: no
